posts.post_title: 41 card T206's low grade lot only 1 double
posts.post_content: Selling my entire T206 collection. Every card was bought from a fellow forum member. I am selling because when I joined the forum I got the T206 bug and it has left the building. Nice set just not for me. Looking to sell all at once if possible. $420 shipped for the lot., it is a little less than I have in them.
Moved this entire lot to the live auctions section with a $1 start price.
